name: Dipped Triangle Necklace
description:

The necklace hangs in the middle of the chest. If you would like a specific length of chain e-mail me at obscurealternativesblog@gmail.com

Each necklace takes about two days to make so please be patient when ordering.

Worn with Obesity & Speed KiL tank
